'''格雷格·伊根'''（{{lang-en|'''Greg Egan'''}}，{{bd|1961年|8月20日||}}），是澳大利亞[[科幻小說|科幻小說]]作家、業餘[[數學家|數學家]]，以其[[硬科幻|硬科幻]]作品而聞名。伊根曾獲多個獎項，包括{{le|約翰·坎貝爾紀念科幻小說最佳小說獎|John W. Campbell Memorial Award for Best Science Fiction Novel}}、[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]及[[軌跡獎|軌跡獎]]。

== 生平及成就 ==
伊根拥有[[西澳大学|西澳大学]]数学科学学士学位。<ref name=burnham>{{cite book|last1=Burnham|first1=Karen|isbn=978-0-252-07993-1|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lPAwAwAAQBAJ&q=greg+egan+Bachelor+of+Science+degree+in+Mathematics&pg=PA1|access-date=1 December 2015|title=Greg Egan|date=30 April 2014|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109062818/https://books.google.com/books?id=lPAwAwAAQBAJ&q=greg+egan+Bachelor+of+Science+degree+in+Mathematics&pg=PA1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Booker|first1=M. Keith|title=Historical Dictionary of Science Fiction in Literature|isbn=978-0810849389|page=98|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WRi7BAAAQBAJ&q=greg+egan+Bachelor+of+Science+degree+in+Mathematics&pg=PA98|access-date=1 December 2015|date=1 October 2014|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109062818/https://books.google.com/books?id=WRi7BAAAQBAJ&q=greg+egan+Bachelor+of+Science+degree+in+Mathematics&pg=PA98|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.student.uwa.edu.au/course/award-verification-service?family=Egan&given=Greg&given_partial=on&search=Search|title=UWA Award Verification Service|access-date=19 March 2018|archive-date=2018-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319163225/http://www.student.uwa.edu.au/course/award-verification-service?family=Egan&given=Greg&given_partial=on&search=Search|dead-url=no}}</ref>

伊根于1983年发表了他的第一部作品。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gregegan.net/BIBLIOGRAPHY/Bibliography.html |title=Bibliography |publisher=Gregegan.net |date=7 August 2014 |access-date=23 August 2014 |archive-date=2021-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217115517/https://www.gregegan.net/BIBLIOGRAPHY/Bibliography.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他专门研究具有[[数学|数学]]和[[量子力學詮釋|量子本体论]]主题的[[硬科幻|硬科幻]]小说，包括[[意识|意识]]的本质。 其他主题包括[[遗传学|遗传学]]、[[模拟现实|模拟现实]]、[[后人类主义|后人类主义]]、[[思想上传|思想上传]]、[[性|性]]、[[人工智能|人工智能]]以及[[理性|理性]][[自然主义|自然主义]]对[[宗教|宗教]]的优越性。他经常处理复杂的技术材料，例如新物理学和流行病学。他是[[雨果奖|雨果奖]]得主（其他八部作品入围了雨果奖），还获得了{{le|约翰·坎贝尔纪念科幻小说最佳小说奖|John W. Campbell Memorial Award for Best Science Fiction Novel}}。他的早期故事具有超自然恐怖的强烈元素。

伊根的短篇小说已在各种类型的杂志上发表，包括定期出現在{{le|Interzone|Interzone (magazine)}}和[[阿西莫夫科幻小说|阿西莫夫科幻小说]]上。

=== 数学 ===
在2018年，伊根设计了一种算法来产生[[超排列|超排列]]，从而为其长度设定了上限。 在2019年2月27日，伊根运用罗宾·休斯敦（Robin Houston）等人的想法，实现了n = 7个长度为5906的符号的超排列，打破了先前的记录。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Egan |first1=Greg |title=Superpermutations |url=https://www.gregegan.net/SCIENCE/Superpermutations/Superpermutations.html |access-date=2 February 2019 |archive-date=2021-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211224040058/https://www.gregegan.net/SCIENCE/Superpermutations/Superpermutations.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Klarreich |first1=Erica |title=Mystery Math Whiz and Novelist Advance Permutation Problem |url=https://www.quantamagazine.org/sci-fi-writer-greg-egan-and-anonymous-math-whiz-advance-permutation-problem-20181105/ |website=[[Quanta_Magazine|Quanta Magazine]] |date=5 November 2018 |access-date=13 May 2019 |archive-date=2021-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003162611/https://www.quantamagazine.org/sci-fi-writer-greg-egan-and-anonymous-math-whiz-advance-permutation-problem-20181105/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 個人生活 ==
截至2015年，伊根都居住在[[珀斯|珀斯]]。伊根是一名[[素食主義|素食主義者]]<ref name=burnham/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gregegan.net/ZENDEGI/IranTrip/IranTrip2.html |title=Iran Trip Diary: Part 2, Esfahan |last=Egan |first=Greg |publisher=Gregegan.net |date=19 October 2008 |access-date=23 August 2014 |archive-date=2021-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109133021/https://www.gregegan.net/ZENDEGI/IranTrip/IranTrip2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[無神論|無神論者]]。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Egan |first1=Greg |editor1-last=Blackford |editor1-first=Russell |editor2-last=Schüklenk |editor2-first=Udo |title=50 Voices of Disbelief: Why We Are Atheists |date=2009 |publisher=Wiley–Blackwell |location=Sussex |chapter-url=https://www.gregegan.net/ESSAYS/BAB/BAB.html |chapter=Born Again, Briefly |access-date=2021-11-09 |archive-date=2021-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109210035/https://www.gregegan.net/ESSAYS/BAB/BAB.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

伊根不參加任何科幻小說大會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gregegan.net/INTERVIEWS/Interviews.html |title=Interviews |first=Russell |last=Farr |publisher=Gregegan.net |date=September 1997 |access-date=23 August 2014 |archive-date=2021-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211030215154/http://www.gregegan.net/INTERVIEWS/Interviews.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>也不簽書，並表示他沒在網路上留下任何照片<ref name=egan>{{cite web |url=https://www.gregegan.net/images/GregEgan.htm |title=Photos of Greg Egan, science fiction writer |publisher=Gregegan.net |access-date=23 August 2014 |archive-date=2021-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210930083154/http://www.gregegan.net/images/GregEgan.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，儘管SF粉絲網站與[[Google搜索|Google搜索]]有時會誤將其他同名同姓人物的照片作為他的照片。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gregegan.net/ESSAYS/GOOGLE/Google.html |title=Google, the Stupidity Amplifier |last=Egan |first=Greg |publisher=Gregegan.net |date=24 August 2012 |access-date=23 August 2014 |archive-date=2021-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210927160843/http://www.gregegan.net/ESSAYS/GOOGLE/Google.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 獎項 ==
* 《{{le|置換城市|Permutation City}}》：{{le|約翰·坎貝爾紀念獎|John W. Campbell Memorial Award for Best Science Fiction Novel}}（1995年）
* 《大洋》：[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]、[[軌跡獎|軌跡獎]]、阿西莫夫讀者獎（1999年）
* 《{{le|傷痛|Distress (novel)}}》：{{le|庫爾德·拉斯維茨最佳外國小說獎|Kurd-Laßwitz-Preis}}（2000年）

伊根的作品曾七次獲得日本[[星雲獎_(日本)|星雲獎]]的最佳翻譯小說獎。

《{{le|特雷尼西亞|Teranesia}}》贏得2000年{{le|迪特瑪獎|Ditmar Award}}最佳小說獎，但伊根拒絕接受該獎項。

